OL,3,CNottingham attacks killer should have
OL,4,Csentence changed, court hears
OL,6,FThe knifeman who should have his
OL,7,Fsentence changed, the Court of Appeal
OL,8,Fhas heard.
OL,10,FValdo Calocane, 32, stabbed university
OL,11,Fstudents Barnaby Webber, 19, Grace
OL,12,FO'Malley-Kumar, 19, and school
OL,13,Fcaretaker Ian Coates, 65,
OL,15,FIn January, Calocane was given an
OL,16,Findefinite hospital order for
OL,17,Fmanslaughter by diminished
OL,18,Fresponsibility, after Nottingham Crown
OL,19,FCourt heard he had been diagnosed with
OL,20,Fparanoid schizophrenia.
