OL,3,CNottingham attacks killer should have
OL,4,Csentence changed, court hears
OL,6,FShe said: "The exceptional level of
OL,7,Fseriousness of the offences was such
OL,8,Fthat the case required the imposition
OL,9,Fof a sentence with a penal element, an
OL,10,Felement of punishment.
OL,12,F"The harm caused and the harm risked
OL,13,Fto members of the public by his crimes
OL,14,Fwas extreme."
OL,16,FSeveral members of the victims'
OL,17,Ffamilies and friends attended the
OL,18,Fhearing at the Royal Courts of Justice
OL,19,Fwhile Calocane attended via video link
OL,20,Ffrom Ashworth high-security hospital
OL,21,Fnear Liverpool.
