OL,6,FIf judges rule that a hybrid order
OL,7,Fshould be imposed, they will set the
OL,8,Flength of time which Calocane should
OL,9,Fbe in custody, with his release then
OL,10,Fgoverned by the Parole Board.
OL,12,FThe hearing before the Lady Chief
OL,13,FJustice Baroness Carr, Lord Justice
OL,14,FEdis and Mr Justice Garnham is set to
OL,15,Fconclude on Wednesday, with a judgment
OL,16,Fdue at a later date.
